#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json
msgid ""
"Batteries, fuel, irons, medicines...All right. Munitions are the best, they "
"are preferred. I have edible things to trade. Do not think of robbing anyone"
" here. We are all armed. Anyway, Let's Trade?"
msgstr ""
"電池、燃料、鐵器、藥品……好吧。彈藥是最好的，我們更青睞這些。我有可食用的東西可以交易。別想著在這裡搶劫任何人。我們都武裝好了。總之，來交易嗎？"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json
msgid ""
"Batteries, fuel, irons, medicines...All right. Munitions are the best, "
"preferred. I have edible things to trade. Do not think of robbing anyone "
"here. We are all armed. Anyway, Let's Trade?"
msgstr "電池、燃料、鐵器、藥品……好吧。彈藥是最好的，更受青睞。我有可食用的東西可以交易。別想著在這裡搶劫任何人。我們都武裝好了。總之，來交易嗎？"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json
#: .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "Is there anything I can help with?"
msgstr "有什麼我能幫忙的嗎？"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json
msgid "Let's see what you have got..."
msgstr "讓我看看你有什麼……"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json
#: .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "bye."
msgstr "再見。"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json
msgid "Nope."
msgstr "不。"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Food.json .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "明白了。"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json
msgid ""
"Another survivor it is. I'm trading some military supplies and munitions "
"smuggled from one of the camps nearby. You wanna trade?"
msgstr "又是一個倖存者。我在交易一些從附近營地走私來的軍用物資和彈藥。你想交易嗎？"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Mil.json .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "No."
msgstr "不。"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "Makeshift firearms, tools, armors. What do you need?"
msgstr "簡易火器、工具、護甲。你需要什麼？"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "Do you take forging commisions?"
msgstr "你接鍛造委託嗎？"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json
msgid "Let's trade."
msgstr "我們來交易吧。"

#: .\TALK_Merc_Smith.json .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr "再見。"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json
msgid ""
"Hey, you'll need some ammo to survive out there. What kind of ammo do you "
"like? You prefer hand-reloaded, or military standard?"
msgstr "嘿，你在外面生存需要一些彈藥。你喜歡哪種彈藥？你更喜歡手工重裝的，還是軍用標準的？"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "I have came here to trade."
msgstr "我是來交易的。"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Ammo.json .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "No, thanks."
msgstr "不，謝謝。"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Bro.json
msgid "<greet>, Where did you come from? Came here to trade?"
msgstr "<greet>，你從哪裡來？是來交易的嗎？"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "<greet>, I deal with diseases and drugs. Want to buy some?"
msgstr "<greet>，我經營疾病和藥物。想買一些嗎？"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Are you a doctor? Can you treat me?"
msgstr "你是醫生嗎？你能治療我嗎？"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid "Let's see what you got..."
msgstr "讓我看看你有什麼……"

#: .\Talk_Merc_Med.json
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, I'm not a real doctor. He died somewhat recently... I'm just "
"selling some of his possessions."
msgstr "不幸的是，我不是真正的醫生。他最近去世了……我只是在賣他的一些遺物。"

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid "Halt! Identify yourself."
msgstr "站住！報上名來。"

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid "I'm just passing. What is this place?"
msgstr "我只是路過。這是什麼地方？"

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid ""
"Another survivor? <greet>. Here is... the Settlement. And maybe the Hub of "
"caravans now. If you want to barter something, Then get in and check it out."
" Also, if you are considering to rob us... I will not recommend it. Unless "
"you are willing to take 7.62mm bullets."
msgstr ""
"又一個倖存者？<greet>。這裡是……定居點。現在可能也是商隊的樞紐。如果你想交易什麼，那就進來看看吧。另外，如果你考慮搶劫我們……我不建議你這麼做。除非你願意吃7.62毫米子彈。"

#: .\Talk_Merc_guard_gate.json
msgid "Got it. Thanks."
msgstr "明白了。謝謝。"

