#: .\merchantitem.json
msgid "Caravan Bag"
msgid_plural "Caravan Bags"
msgstr[0] "商隊揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Caravan Bag'}
#: .\merchantitem.json
msgid ""
"The luggage, often used by caravans. It is too bulky to carry. However, when"
" it comes to trade in one area, this is one of the most perfect storage."
msgstr "商隊常用的行李。過於笨重不便攜帶。然而，若在某一區域進行貿易，這是最完美的儲存容器之一。"

#: .\merchantitem.json
msgid "dead lightstrip"
msgid_plural "dead lightstrips"
msgstr[0] "損壞的燈條"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dead lightstrip'}
#: .\merchantitem.json
msgid "A broken, non-functional lightstrip. Cannot be used for anything."
msgstr "一條損壞、無法使用的燈條。無法用於任何用途。"

