#. ~ Profession (male Novice Scavenger) description
#: .\profession.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"The Novice Scavenger who came out from the hometown a minute ago. Still "
"everything at 'Outside wasteland' is embarrassing. It seems I need to get "
"some weapons like pipe rifles by trading something."
msgstr "剛剛從家鄉出來的新手拾荒者。對'外部廢土'的一切仍感到窘迫。看來我需要通過交易獲取一些武器，比如管式步槍。"

