#: .\profession.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Wasteland Ranger"
msgstr "廢土遊俠"

#: .\profession.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Wasteland Ranger"
msgstr "廢土遊俠"

#. ~ Profession (male Wasteland Ranger) description
#: .\profession.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"If the human race is to survive, the threats facing its existence must be "
"eliminated, no matter the cost.  If it's hostile, you kill it."
msgstr "若人類想要生存下去，就必須不惜一切代價消除威脅其存在的因素。只要是敵對的，就將其消滅。"

#. ~ Profession (female Wasteland Ranger) description
#: .\profession.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
