msgstr "若人類想要生存下去，就必須不惜一切代價消除威脅其存在的因素。只要是敵對的，就將其消滅。"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Village Dweller' for a male character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Village Dweller"
msgstr "村民"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Village Dweller' for a female character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Village Dweller"
msgstr "村民"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Village Dweller' for a male character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Some years have passed from the cataclysm. I learned some skills to survive "
"in wasteland by my parents, who are not living now. And now, I have to get "
"out from the hometown to get supplies, like my predecessors did."
msgstr "大災變已過去數年。我從已故的父母那裡學到了一些在廢土生存的技能。如今，我必須像前輩們一樣離開家鄉去獲取補給。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Village Dweller' for a female character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
